snippet.title: Chicken Jump - App Preview
snippet.description:
A crazy local multiplayer jumping game, now available on mobiles and tablets! Download for free: iOS (http://apple.co/2iHtjtV) / Android (https://goo.gl/gCpHtu).

Chicken Jump is an easy to grab and funny party game set in a town like no other, in which residents celebrate by jumping over waves of wacky traffic. Avoid being crushed as long as you can by jumping at the right time and get the highest score in town to impress your friends! 

Developed by Firepunchd - http://firepunchd.com/
More info at: http://playdigious.com/chicken-jump/
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playdigious
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playdigious
